---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---

    {% set textGradientOnHover = "transition bg-clip-text hover:text-transparent active:text-transparent animate-gradient-fast" %}

<div id="scroll-container" class="px-small md:px-medium lg:px-large box-border xs:snap-proximity xs:snap-y w-screen h-screen overflow-y-auto">
    <nav class="flex flex-col justify-between pt-small md:pt-medium snap-center lg:pt-large box-border h-screen relative">
        <div>
            <p id="top" class="animate-in text-3xl mb-4 font-light">Hugo Sundberg</p>
            <h1 class="animate-in text-7xl font-bold md:text-8xl">Portfolio.</h1>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li class="animate-in mb-4"><a class="bg-gradientDarkRed {{textGradientOnHover}} text-3xl font-bold" data-en="Projects" href="#projects">Projekt</a></li>
            <li class="animate-in mb-4"><a class="bg-gradientDarkBlue {{textGradientOnHover}} text-3xl font-bold" data-en="About me" href="#about-me">Om mig</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="animate-in flex items-center gap-1 mb-10">
            <img class="h-4" src="images/icons/lang.svg" alt="">
            <button id="language-switch" class="w-fit underline" data-en="Byt till svenska" href="">Switch to english</button>
        </div>
    </nav>
    {% set imageBaseStyle = "object-cover image lg:h-[58vh] h-[30vh] xs:h-[48vh] w-full max-w-[1024px]" %}
    {% set textCardBaseStyle = "translate-y-[200px] backdrop-blur-lg shadow-card bg-white/80 relative p-card-small md:p-card-medium lg:p-card-large -mt-small md:-mt-medium lg:-mt-large w-full max-w-[460px] rounded-card-medium bg-white shall-animate" %}
    {% set techContainerBaseStyle = "absolute top-[10px] flex gap-[10px]" %}
    {% set techImageBaseStyle = "hover:rotate-6 transition duration-300 relative invisible xs:visible h-16 w-16 rounded-icon-medium object-cover" %}
    {% for project in projects %}
    {% set imageSrc = project.images[0].path %}
    <section {% if(loop.first) %} id="projects" {% endif %} class="relative mb-8 xs:mb-0 xs:h-screen snap-start w-full flex items-center">
        <div class="w-full">
            {% if loop.index % 2 == 0 %}
        {# Image to right #}
                <div class="max-w-[1024px] ml-auto relative translate-x-small md:translate-x-medium lg:translate-x-large right-0 w-full">
                    <div class="{{techContainerBaseStyle}} left-[10px]">
                        {% for technnology in project.technnologies %}
                            <a href="{{technnology.url}}"><img class="{{techImageBaseStyle}}" src="{{technnology.path}}" alt="{{technnology.name}}"></a> 
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <img class="{{imageBaseStyle}} ml-auto rounded-image-medium-right" src="{{imageSrc}}" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="{{textCardBaseStyle}} ml-auto">
            {% else %} 
        {# Image to left #}
                 <div class="max-w-[1024px] relative -ml-small md:-ml-medium lg:-ml-large left-0 w-full">
                    <div class="{{techContainerBaseStyle}} right-[10px]">
                        {% for technnology in project.technnologies %}
                            <a href="{{technnology.url}}"><img class="{{techImageBaseStyle}}" src="{{technnology.path}}" alt="{{technnology.name}}"></a> 
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                    <img class="{{imageBaseStyle}} rounded-image-medium" src="{{imageSrc}}" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="{{textCardBaseStyle}}">
            {% endif %}
                <p data-en="{{project.description.en}}">{{project.description.sv}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {% endfor %}
    <section id="about-me" class="xs:h-screen snap-start flex flex-col gap-3 md:gap-4 aboutMeBreak:items-center justify-center">
        <div class="flex-col-reverse aboutMeBreak:flex-row flex gap-3 md:gap-8">
            <img class="max-w-[366px] object-cover rounded-card-medium shadow-card-small h-[20vh] xs:h-[25vh] md:h-[40vh]" src="images/me.jpg" alt="">
            <h2 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-8xl font-bold mt-4" data-en="About me">Om mig.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class=" backdrop-blur-lg shadow-card bg-white/80 relative p-card-small md:p-card-medium lg:p-card-large w-full max-w-[580px] rounded-card-medium bg-white shall-animate">
            <h3>Hugo Sundberg</h3>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Turpis egestas pretium aenean pharetra. Orci eu lobortis elementum nibh tellus molestie. Vulputate dignissim suspendisse in est. Vel pharetra vel turpis nunc. Malesuada nunc vel risus commodo. Nisi vitae suscipit tellus mauris. Posuere morbi leo urna molestie at elementum eu. Urna duis convallis convallis tellus. Urna molestie at elementum eu. Nunc sed blandit libero volutpat.</p>
            <div>
                <img src="images/icons/site-icon.svg" alt="">
                <p data-en="Visit the site" >Besök sidan</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="images/icons/gh-icon.svg" alt="">
                <p data-en="Or check out the github repository" >Eller kolla in repot på github</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>